"{\"uid\": \"thewrap.com-salma-hayek-paris-olympics-summer-games-torch-relay\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was proud to represent the enduring spirit of the Olympics, bringing light, hope and unity to all,\\\" the actress says ahead of the opening ceremony  Salma Hayek celebrated being one of the 11,000 people selected to be torchbearers for theParis 2024 Olympicand Paralympic torch relays ahead of this weekend's Summer Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Hayek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salma Hayek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Hayek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Hayek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Black Mirror\\\" actress joined 174 other select individuals as they brought the flame from Rambouillet, France, to Le ch\\u00e2teau de Versailles on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Mirror\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.426684227130076e-19, \"text\": \"Black Mirror\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Mirror\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Mirror\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.468680779227363e-13, \"text\": \"Rambouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rambouillet\"}, {\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999978822416, \"rank\": 1.982430455495232e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ch\\u00e2teau de Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's torch was first lit in\\u00a0Olympia, Greece, on April 16 and will ultimately land at Paris' Jardins du Trocad\\u00e9ro stadium on Friday.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia, Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia, Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1231799119628204e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yesterday, I had the honor of carrying the Olympic flame, a symbol of light, hope, peace and unity.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you believe in these values, know that you were with me every step of the way,\\\" Hayek shared onInstagramWednesday.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued, \\\"As I passed the torch and took part in the relay, I was proud to represent the enduring spirit of the Olympics, bringing light, hope and unity to all.\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only does the wife of Fran\\u00e7ois-Henri Pinault have French citizenship herself, in 2011, Hayek was given the country's highest honorific as a chevalier in the National Order of the Legion of Honour.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois-Henri_Pinault\", \"score\": 0.9999999993183337, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fran\\u00e7ois-Henri Pinault\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois-Henri_Pinault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois-Henri_Pinault\"}, {\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_nationality_law\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French citizenship\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_nationality_law\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_nationality_law\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friedrich_Hayek\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2458190573243876e-12, \"text\": \"Hayek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q188094\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friedrich_Hayek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Friedrich_Hayek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other notable names taking part in this year's torch relay include Patrick Bruel, Stefanos Douskos, Laure and Florent Manaudou, Mona Francis, Dimitri Pavad\\u00e9, Rachida Dati, Mathieu Forget, Presnel Kimpembe and Snoop Dogg.Per the official games'website, \\\"The torchbearers [were] selected based on their commitment, dedication and how they embody at least one of the core tenets of Paris 2024\\\" - sport, community and the collective.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"scor